metadata.name: After the rain
metadata.description:
It's been one year since I minted my first artwork on Foundation. I've never thought this was the start of a journey that would change my life. I'm so grateful for all the artists and collectors I met during the last year.

I want to celebrate this one year anniversary with a special drop.

Every wallet that bids on this artwork will receive a free commemorative NFT from me.

Thank you so much to everyone who supported me!

I can't wait to see what the next 365 days will bring me.
